

	 
      i noticed the first pieces of white hair on my dad today. they're starting to sneak their way into his eyebrows as well. it made me really sad and want to give him a great big bear hug. he'd prepared tomorrow's breakfast lunch and dinner for me even though i couldn't eat dinner with him for the fourth night in a row. he even saved for me the last piece of cheesecake, his favorite food in the whole wide world. my sweet sweet papa bear. 
     
    
